query:
SELECT t.id, t.codigo, t.curso, t.instituicao, COUNT(e.id) as numEventos
FROM turmas t
JOIN eventos e ON e.turmaId = t.id
GROUP BY t.id
HAVING numEventos > 0
ORDER BY t.codigo
LIMIT 10
